text: ON THEIR WAY: More than 1,000 baby Taricaya turtles were released into a river in Peru's Amazon region over the weekend. The species has become vulnerable due to poaching and human activities. https://t.co/Ue6HahfXm2 https://t.co/4BSm9fWyB3
